headline: Netformx® Officially Launches AssetXpert™, Empowering Cisco Partners with Flexible Network Discovery and Actionable Insights
summary: Netformx® today announced the official launch of AssetXpert™, following a successful trial introduction with Cisco Partners. AssetXpert gives IT solution providers the ability to quickly and accurately assess a customer's actual network state, streamline End-of-Life (EoX) tracking, and unlock insights that drive technology refreshes, security posture improvements, and managed services opportunities.

headline: Cisco Introduces Agentic Capabilities for Next-Generation Collaboration
summary: Today at WebexOne 2025, Cisco (NASDAQ: CSCO) unveiled solutions to foster dynamic collaboration between people and AI agents in the workplace. This includes new agentic capabilities in Cisco AI Assistant, RoomOS 26 for Cisco Devices, and purpose-built integrations across Cisco devices and the Webex Suite to help organizations easily manage and work seamlessly with digital agents.

headline: Cisco Unveils Advanced AI-Powered Webex Contact Center Solutions and Industry Integrations
summary: Cisco (NASDAQ: CSCO) today announced enhancements to the Webex Customer Experience portfolio, including a new AI-powered tool for supervisors launching in early 2026 to unify quality management across the contact center. Cisco also unveiled AI customer momentum, deep industry integrations for seamless and secure experiences, and planned Webex ecosystem expansions in India and the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.
